00:08:33.879 --> 00:08:34.919
I can't thank you enough.

00:08:35.759 --> 00:08:36.360
Don't worry about it.

00:08:36.360 --> 00:08:36.840
I am willing—

00:08:36.919 --> 00:08:37.559
It's really nothing.

00:08:37.559 --> 00:08:38.600
I'm willing to give myself to you.

00:08:38.600 --> 00:08:39.519
I said it's nothing.

00:08:41.120 --> 00:08:42.080
Give yourself to him?

00:08:43.440 --> 00:08:44.039
Miss,

00:08:44.279 --> 00:08:45.960
Young ladies shouldn't say things like that.

00:08:46.159 --> 00:08:47.279
It sounds terrible if word gets out.

00:08:47.399 --> 00:08:48.360
Isn't it? No, you—you—

00:08:48.360 --> 00:08:49.480
Who are you? Yeah!

00:08:49.559 --> 00:08:49.960
You—

00:08:50.039 --> 00:08:51.080
