00:09:00.840 --> 00:09:02.320
We had a childhood engagement.

00:09:02.759 --> 00:09:04.240
I was so young, how could I remember?

00:09:07.639 --> 00:09:08.200
Forget it.

00:09:08.320 --> 00:09:10.240
I'll let you go for solving the case.

00:09:13.200 --> 00:09:14.200
